um....
that's weird
i swear i hear something..
something that sounds like...
a hearing sensation similar to.....
almost as if........
it sounds almost exactly like............

an ungodly number

hypothetically
of course
because such a number of pistachio shells is highly unlikely to converge at any given point in space and time
so it must be something else
but just to be safe. i probably shouldn't go opening that door
